Package: rotations
Type: Package
Title: Tools for working with rotational data
Version: 0.1
Author: Bryan Stanfill <stanfill@iastate.edu>, Heike Hofmann
    <hofmann@iastate.edu>, Ulrike Genschel <ulrike@iastate.edu>
Maintainer: Bryan Stanfill <stanfill@iastate.edu>
Description: This package implements tools for working with rotational data: it
    allows simulation from the most commonly used distributions on the sphere,
    it estimates differen mean and median type estimators for the main
    direction of a number of rotations, it provides (bootstrap) confidence
    regions for the estimates, and it allows to visualize rotational data.
License: MIT
Collate:
    'help.R'
    'class.R'
    'simulate.R'
